data.description: CURRENTLY UNDER CONTRACT, SELLER WILL CONSIDER BACKUP OFFERS! Back on market, no fault of the sellers! Welcome to the highly desired area of Lynn Haven! Here's your chance to own a gorgeous well maintained home on a quiet, centrally located street that is move-in ready! You will be close to shopping, entertainment, and a plethora of restaurants for your dining pleasures. Enjoy the homey features of this 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home such as the soft close cabinets and drawers in the kitchen and bathroom vanities, newer appliances and fixtures, ring doorbell, hurricane windows, newer sprinkler system, and the garage work area! This home also has vaulted ceilings in the living room accompanied by a wood fireplace, vinyl plank flooring, quartz counter tops in the kitchen and bathrooms, as well as a spacious enclosed sun room to entertain your guest, family and closest friends! Cap the night of by roasting marshmallows beside the custom fire pit in the luscious green backyard! The French drain and sump pump were installed in February 2021 in the backyard for drainage from elevated leach field.The A/C unit (inside and outside) were inspected and serviced July 2023. Sellers are motivated!!!!Call your favorite realtor today to take a tour!
